<ul class="breadcrumbs">
  <li><a href="/?showLabels={{showLabels}}">Hem</a></li>
  <li>Kategori: {{categoryLabel}}</li>
</ul>

<h1>{{categoryLabel}}</h1>

<div class="display-mode">
  <label for="displayToggle">Visa mänskligt läsbara etiketter:</label>
  <label class="switch">
    <input type="checkbox" id="displayToggle" {{#if showLabels}}checked{{/if}}>
    <span class="slider"></span>
  </label>
  <span class="display-mode-text">{{#if showLabels}}På{{else}}Av{{/if}}</span>
</div>

<p>Visar alla resurser i kategorin <strong>{{categoryLabel}}</strong>. Klicka på en resurs för att visa detaljerad information.</p>

<div class="resource-metadata">
  <p>Kategori URI: <code>{{categoryUri}}</code></p>
</div>

<h2>Resurser</h2>

<ul class="resource-list">
  {{#each resources}}
    <li>
      <div class="resource-list-item">
        <span class="resource-icon {{getIconClass this.label}}"></span>
        <a href="/resource?uri={{encodeURIComponent this.uri}}&showLabels={{../showLabels}}">
          {{this.label}}
        </a>
      </div>
    </li>
  {{/each}}

  {{#unless resources.length}}
    <li>❌ Inga resurser hittades i denna kategori.</li>
  {{/unless}}
</ul>

<a href="/?showLabels={{showLabels}}" class="btn">Tillbaka till alla kategorier</a>
<a href="/resource?uri={{encodeURIComponent categoryUri}}&showLabels={{showLabels}}" class="btn">Visa kategoriinformation</a>